<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَسْمَاءٌ لَازَمَتِ النِّدَاءَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥٩٥. وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«فُلُ»</span> بَعْضُ مَا يُخَصُّ بِالنِّدَا … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لُؤْمَانُ، نَوْمَانُ»</span> كَذَا، وَاطَّرَدَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٥٩٦. فِي سَبِّ الُانْثَى وَزْنُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«يَا خَبَاثِ!»</span> … وَالْأَمْرُ هَكَذَا مِنَ الثُّلَاثِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٥٩٧. وَشَاعَ فِي سَبِّ الذُّكُورِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«فُعَلُ»</span> … وَلَا تَقِسْ، وَجُرَّ فِي الشِّعْرِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«فُلُ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>